item.description: /* Upload image dialog */ .uploadimage-dragndrop { border: 2px dashed #DDD; margin: 20px 0; padding: 50px 20px; text-align: center; color: #DDD; } .uploadimage-text { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 20px; } .uploadimage-input { margin: 20px 0; } .uploadimage-upload { background: #EEE; margin: 4px 0; } .uploadimage-uploadcompleted { background: #d1f4ac; } .uploadimage-fileinfo { padding: 5px; font-size: 11px; position: relative; } .uploadimage-progresspct { position: absolute; top: 5px; right: 5px; } .uploadimage-progress { background: #999; } .
